[Band Aid 30, the 2014 update of the Band Aid campaign that raised money for [famine in] Ethiopia in 1984, has raised over GBP 1 million (USD 1.5 million) for Ebola within 5 minutes of being launched. The updated version of "Do They Know It's Christmas?," which features One Direction, Ed Sheeran, Ellie Goulding, and Sam Smith, among others, was recorded in London [UK] on Sat [15 Nov 2014], and the video premiered [on TV] on Sun [16 Nov 2014]'s X Factor http://mashable.com/2014/11/17/band-aid-30-single. - Mod.JW]

