[5] Thailand
Date: 17 Nov 2014
From: Nyles Bauer <nyles314@hotmail.com> [edited]


Surprisingly, there is great concern about Ebola here in Thailand. Not much on TV, but walking through the airport was reminiscent of the time of avian influenza, when I was also in the region, but the concerns far more justified.

